{"tid":2228800,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"（日本人都幾搞笑）「失去石原聰美」社會現象","createTime":"2020-10-04T00:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T05:29:15.000Z","uid":36494,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"62ab5da8f00f2c7cdfb1278d4fd76ba6d72b52ad","tid":2228800,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T00:55:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/entertainment/lost-satomi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fentertainment%2Flost-satomi%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdmrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=fadf1e00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/entertainment/lost-satomi/</a><br />\n<br />\n文中節錄<br />\n<br />\n「已經不行了，明天去不了公司」<br />\n<br />\n「我的支柱已經消失了」<br />\n<br />\n前AKB成員現為鋼琴演奏家的松井咲子目擊有人在電車中一邊碎碎念「認真的嗎&hellip;」一邊抱頭的搞笑畫面！<br />\n<br />\n「雖然我知道你是戀愛中的女人這個傳聞，但竟然&hellip;剩下的希望就只有gakki（新垣結衣）了&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「我們不是還有gakki嗎」<br />\n<br />\n「和石原聰美結婚的普通男性，給朋友看她的照片說這是我女朋友，應該也會被當作開玩笑吧&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「和上司報告『我要和石原聰美結婚』也會被以為是工作忙昏頭了吧，我會忍不住這樣想像。笑」<br />\n<br />\n「和普通人結婚這件事，因為我也是普通人，所以實質上就是我和石原聰美結婚了對吧。話說我現在才知道。」<br />\n<br />\n「回到家看到這麼可愛的老婆甚麼的，和石原結婚的普通男性太過人生勝利組了吧」"},{"pid":"29d7c76ba3d40db1fa5a20ec9a346b9a6def685d","tid":2228800,"uid":231583,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T01:12:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b23e2e819a1f32f75bed04da1fe1cf1ef861373","tid":2228800,"uid":185651,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T01:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/17/Q1fr9I.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2FQ1fr9I.gif&h=f7cf18df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e0425dfb9ee39351ff513dc061402adb0404c3d","tid":2228800,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T01:16:08.000Z","msg":"我覺得依一代嘅日本女星應該會陸陸續續咁宣佈結婚，到時日本......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />